post_text:
Hey Friends, there has been much discussion and weighing of options regarding the Bobcat Quarter Auction. Babysitters have been secured, the basket prizes are brimming and per the Governor our total head count is under 250. Ticket sales continue to happen, all that to say The Sports Boosters board has decided to go forward with holding the auction on Saturday, March 14th. Doors at the lake holiday lodge will open at 6:00 pm. the auction will start at 7:00. There are still a few tickets left for at the door purchase. We sincerely hope we‚Äôve made the right decision and that you will all be able to join us. In trying to be sensitive to all opinions, refunds will be honored on presale tickets up until the doors open at 6 PM. If you feel you need a refund please get in touch with a boosters member before 6 PM tomorrow. Once the doors open, we will not be able to issue ticket refunds. Again we hope to see everyone there.Ôøº

***let us know in the comments if you plan to join us!
